      EggMind @eggmind2026 的证明派生记忆用相对收益更新 motif 评分。对候选案例 $c$ 和 motif $gamma$，核心更新可写为：
      $
        g(c) = max(0, 1 - "final-cost"(c) / "previous-best-cost"(c))
      $
      $
        "score"(gamma) <- (1 - alpha) "score"(gamma) + alpha g(c)
      $
      $
        "best-gain"(gamma) <- max("best-gain"(gamma), g(c))
      $
    ]
  ]
]

